metadata.name: Eye For An Eye
metadata.description:
It's said an eye for an eye makes the whole world blind. It seems Marge, blind with fury in her quest for vengeance, has unwittingly found herself at the mercy of none other than escaped convict and notorious serial murderer “Sideshow” Bobu. It’s not looking good for our favorite blue-haired femme fatale. Will she make it out alive? Or does her path of revenge end at the edge of a psycho killer’s blade?

Find out next time on MARGE: Assassin
